{"type": "article", "id": 35140, "title": "想用芝士玩出花样？这把枪可以满足你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-01T23:09:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35425, "name": "Yonoh Creative Studio"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 35421, "name": "INYARD"}, {"id": 35426, "name": "Sami Kallio"}, {"id": 35427, "name": "Ji Lee"}, {"id": 35428, "name": "Juan Carlos Franco"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016120122591856TKPbI9JCFE1Aa3.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Light Bell by Sami Kallio</h3><p>马上就是圣诞节了，来自圣诞老人故乡芬兰的设计师 Sami Kallio 以驯鹿铃为灵感，为<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>设计了一套名为 Light Bell 的灯具。Kallio 希望通过这个形似鹿铃的灯罩，营造出一种温暖的氛围。金属和橡木构成的直线支架和温润的牛皮以及黄铜组合在了一起，朴实自然的风格使灯具相当百搭。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300132\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，台灯和落地灯的售价分别为 496 和 1292 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612012120427NALFUloE8b6HY4c.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212041eoyRMJ68gGNlp0KP.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212044Lq4WRSupT5JeUf7G.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212042zuHxWrkAVj6Ma2Tq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Spoon chair by Yonoh Creative Studio</h3><p>西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.yonoh.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yonoh</a> 以生活中常见的汤匙为灵感，为 <a href=\"http://www.inyard.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">INYARD</a> 设计了这款可拆卸的两半椅。它的椅背和座位为一体，左右两部分采用椅背的圆形金属相连。不过从正面观察，有一种像是通过垫子间的磁性相吸的感觉。在这是它的<a href=\"http://www.inyard.com/cn/products/details?id=10899\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1860 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225551oygirQANRmPu5wTh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225551NyVatLR2wG5srIFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225551NyPkVFA0p9jYc5r2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225552je1fVXuvzEWSwspk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>WISP</h3><p class=\"\">清洁地板时，是不是经常会被扫不干净或是没法扫进畚箕里的灰尘感到烦心？一手拿扫帚一手拿畚箕时间长了是不是觉得有点累？最近一个来自美国的团队对这两件常用工具进行了一次改造，想让你在扫地时轻松一些。WISP 的扫把毛刷被设计成垂直于地面，配套的畚箕则去掉了上方的长柄，可以一手扫地，同时用脚控制畚箕，让它在踩下后更贴合地面以便于收集灰尘。除此之外，畚箕两边还留有清洁毛刷的小口，只要轻轻一刮就能将毛刷上的灰尘留在畚箕里了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/277851410/wisp-the-complete-reimagining-of-the-broom-and-dus\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，套装最低价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000011IoYVpdRBUX2fD7Pr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000010Wwo6zftMjuQaEs8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000010qYFLw0sdKZWIhOvB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000010nHhBEpm9lCVfKaWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000011YjXiOgNHV14obwGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Redundant by Ji Lee</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://pleaseenjoy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ji Lee</a> 是一名在纽约工作的韩裔平面设计师，在他就读帕森斯设计学院（Parsons School of Design）的时候，他为了学校的项目设计了一个挂钟。由于没有产品设计的经验，Lee 制作了一款后就将它的照片放在了网站上，不料之后经常有人邮件询问他如何能购买到这个钟面有些奇特的产品：Redundant 的钟面并没有数字，Lee 选择用 12 个代表它们的小钟面作为替代。最近，Lee 则在热情粉丝的帮助下成功找到了愿意生产的制作商，有望实现量产。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1859831505/redundant-clock\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 49 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000157us7KP1di3f8MkDEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000157mva842SypgXKMQL7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000157Tndu8XDgJt6AHSo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161202000157z9khSqXBslMTw50Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Fondoodler</h3><p>既然有蛋糕裱花枪，为什么不能有一把能挤出芝士的枪呢？最近 BuzzFeed 旗下的 Product Lab 团队就监制了这么一款专为芝士控打造的“武器” Fondoodler。它由三个可拆卸和机洗的部件组成，还附有一个用来清洁残存芝士的刷子。无论是留言、涂鸦还是砌一座饼干塔，这把芝士枪都能满足你的创意。这是它的<a href=\"https://fondoodler.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">订购链接</a>，售价为 24.99 美元。美中不足的是，它暂不发往美国以外的地区。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212139ZnYJ8BilemP6rC3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212136H0QkKORvnrwJBUeF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212139zVRdaQKtTWIMh0Cg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212135xl8Ka1UDuAQ7BH9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.012029\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201212136kzuNhKpE4Cm95xWs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.007183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bookshelf A1 by Juan Carlos Franco</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>就像我们之前做过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32054.html\">特辑</a>那样，书架并不一定得是看上去中规中矩又厚重的家具。设计师 Juan Carlos France 为哥伦比亚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.vrokka.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vrokka</a> 打造的 <a href=\"http://www.vrokka.com/bookshelf-a1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bookshelf A1</a> 就是最近发现的新例。实栎木的支架看上去非常轻盈，有一种独特的骨感美，X 字型交叉结构搭配薄薄的石制搁板也相当协调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225613CuQG8ijmLBvD3hwp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225613ofaL2b3N0cz5jvMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225613zr2nktW40dGhm1QZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161201225613PoTF4lLWJ8NYdMCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>"}